        Installation
        ------------
        
        Greenstalk supports Python 3.5 and later. It's available on the Python Package
        Index and can be installed by running:
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ pip install greenstalk
        
        Getting Started
        ---------------
        
        .. code-block:: pycon
        
            >>> import greenstalk
            >>> queue = greenstalk.Client(host='127.0.0.1', port=11300)
            >>> queue.put('hello')
            1
            >>> job = queue.reserve()
            >>> job.id
            1
            >>> job.body
            'hello'
            >>> queue.delete(job)
            >>> queue.close()
        
